item.title: Need help with my server
item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

when i press start server.. the blk box dispeared... and my server anit eyrescape

Don’t click start server on moparscape, just log in to your server after it’s started. You can’t be running a hybridscape server (the one that moparscape automatically starts when you click “Start Server”) and your server at the same time, that’s why you are having issues.

Also, please do not bump your posts, thanks.
